                <p>Bill Nye, known as "The Science Guy," is an iconic science educator, television personality, and author. He has dedicated his career to making science accessible and engaging for all ages. Through his entertaining shows, public speaking, and educational endeavors, Nye inspires curiosity and promotes scientific literacy worldwide.</p>
